column5: After all this time without fishing, i thought to myself can i get back into fishing and the passion i had for it   It was a long and slow process for myself to even bother casting a line. Sure enough, a few friends and my girls excitement rekindled what was about to burnt out inside me. The thrill, excitement, anticipation, a sleepless night(s)more less, its back and Im back in the game again  Thank you all for your support and pms  This year is going to be a bigger and better year for fishing Todays little guy for you guys to see
Good to have you back, Vince!! Nice brownie
Awesome job Vince   Glad you're back in the groove  but what's up with the goatee    been slacking or what
1 lbs than the last one, but whose counting anyway
Nice going Vince -great way to start the new year  I got a feeling 2012 is gonna be a good year for ya and beat the you know what out of last year.
Nice going Vince!  I love me some Lake O brownies!!!!
Ma Man !!!! Nice fishing Bud !!!! Look at that smile
Nice work Vince. Was another good day out fishing. We will have to get out this weekend again.
I was in the same kinda boat Vince. I cant get enough now,again.  Nice brown.
The best therapy for your troubles is fishing as far as I'm concerned....It beats all else....
Thanks guys  Im sure there will be a few more posts to come before the trolling season starts  Well I hope so for therapy sake
